237
00:18:58,510 --> 00:19:00,076
Isn't your read-through on Thursday?

238
00:19:00,100 --> 00:19:01,746
Yeah. Don't remind me.

239
00:19:01,770 --> 00:19:03,076
It's gonna be great.

240
00:19:03,100 --> 00:19:05,980
