character isn't working.

241
00:19:06,480 --> 00:19:07,996
Can we talk about this later?

242
00:19:08,020 --> 00:19:10,256
Sure. Is shep coming
to my show tonight?

243
00:19:10,280 --> 00:19:11,666
Yeah. Didn't you wanna meet him?

244
